', 'frontend-1', 'emailservice-0', 'currencyservice-2', 'adservice-1', 'cartservice-0'], 'aiops-k8s-08': ['redis-cart-0', 'recommendationservice-0', 'paymentservice-0', 'cartservice-1', 'adservice-2', 'shippingservice-1', 'cartservice-2']}\n\n\n[ANALYSIS STATE]\n\nCurrent Hypothesis: None\n\nCurrent Iteration: 2\n\n\n[AGENT FINDINGS HISTORY]\n\n--- Log Agent Findings ---\n基于采集到的日志数据，我已经完成了对异常事件的分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Unavailable\", \"timed out\", \"i/o timeout\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"connection error\", \"server handshake\", \"shipping quote failure\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice服务出现连接超时和握手超时问题，导致无法提供运输报价服务\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout 和 timed out waiting for server handshake\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**关键发现：**\n1. **错误模式**：所有错误日志都来自frontend服务，错误集中在与shippingservice的连接问题上\n2. **连接问题类型**：\n   - I/O超时：`transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout`\n   - 握手超时：`timed out waiting for server handshake`\n3. **影响范围**：所有frontend实例都受到影响，涉及3个不同的K8s节点\n\n**根因分析：**\n- shippingservice服务（IP: 10.233.27.213, 端口: 50051）在异常时间段内无法正常响应连接请求\n- 这导致frontend服务在调用购物车结算功能时无法获取运输报价，最终导致订单处理失败\n- 问题表现为网络连接层面的超时，可能是shippingservice服务本身出现故障或网络连接问题\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\n基于获取到的指标数据分析，我发现了明显的服务性能异常。让我分析这些异常指标并生成假设。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice-0和shippingservice-1的error_ratio和client_error_ratio从0%飙升到63.16%和53.01%，同时rrt_max和rrt指标出现显著增加，表明该服务出现严重错误和性能下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0: error_ratio从0.0%升至63.16%，rrt_max从1511.0升至2707.0；shippingservice-1: error_ratio从0.0%升至53.01%，表明服务不可用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"checkoutservice-2的rrt从3755.2ms激增至1127722.3ms（增长299倍），rrt_max从113118.0ms增至20052229.0ms，表明该Pod存在严重性能瓶颈\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt指标median_change_ratio=1.9867，p99_change_ratio=1.9937，响应时间异常增长\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务的所有Pod都出现rrt_max和rrt指标显著增加，frontend-0的rrt_max从147754.0ms增至20051681.0ms，同时server_error_ratio增加，表明前端服务受到下游服务影响\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: rrt_max增长135倍，server_error_ratio从0.0%升至0.28%；frontend-1: rrt_max增长125倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n基于获取到的调用链数据，我将进行详细分析。从数据中可以明显看出一个清晰的错误传播路径。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\", \"frontend->checkoutservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-2 (10.233.27.213:50051) 出现连接超时错误：'dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout'，导致所有调用该服务的请求失败\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice-2 调用 shippingservice 的延迟从正常 9.3ms 激增至 21.6秒（延迟倍数 2317倍），因等待shippingservice响应而超时\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend 服务因 checkoutservice 超时而返回 HTTP 500 错误，影响用户下单流程\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现分析**：\n\n1. **根因确定**：shippingservice-2 (IP: 10.233.27.213:50051) 是问题的源头，出现网络连接超时错误。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**：\n   - shippingservice 不可用 → checkoutservice 调用超时 → frontend 返回500错误\n\n3. **延迟影响**：\n   - checkoutservice 调用 shippingservice 的延迟从 9.3ms 增加到 21.6秒\n   - frontend 下单接口延迟从正常 150ms 左右增加到 20+秒\n\n4. **错误类型**：主要是网络连接超时（i/o timeout）和握手超时，表明 shippingservice 可能宕机或网络分区。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "shippingservice-2 (10.233.27.213:50051) is the root cause due to network connection timeout issues, leading to checkout failures across frontend services"}
